Muhammed Şahin (born 1965 in Pazar, Rize) is a Turkish academic. He is the former rector) of Istanbul Technical University (2008-2012), and the founding rector of MEF University (2013 – present).
He was schooled at Pazar Sivritepe Village Primary School, Pazar Secondary School and Pazar High School, Muhammed Şahin graduated from the Department of Geodesy and Photogrammetry (Geomatics) Engineering, Faculty of Civil Engineering, İstanbul Technical University in 1987 at the top of his class.
